
The document "NC Smartcard boot block contents"
(http://om78/ncdocs/bootblock_frame.html) has changed. I'd like you all
to welcome a new bit CLIENT_UPDATE, who'll be taking up position 6 in
SYSTEM_FLAGS(3). CLIENT_UPDATE will be helping us decide whether users
can change their smartcard details from the login screens.

Ant
